title: Wedding Brunch
description:
Starring Lisa Kleinman, Dan Hodapp, Jonathan Marballi, Kelly Hudson, Langan Kingsley,  Avery Monsen, James McCarthy, Kristy Lopez-Bernal, Zack Phillips.

Directed by John Flynn.

From Maude Night at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theatre, August 13, 2012.

Filmed by Alex Aden.
Edited by Curtis Raye.
